## Project Identity

**Trading Dashboard** is a personal trading and options analysis tool built to support Stephen's covered call, wheel strategy, and broader equity/options workflow. It surfaces real-time stock data, options chains, and rule-based filters to identify actionable trades without manual screening.

- **Stage:** Active development
- **Owner:** Stephen (personal use)
- **Primary use case:** Covered call candidate filtering, options chain analysis, wheel strategy execution support

