## API Integrations

### Tiingo (Live Stock Prices)
- Endpoint: IEX real-time feed
- Used for: Live price quotes on screened tickers
- Client: `backend/app/services/tiingo_service.py`
- Docs: https://api.tiingo.com/documentation/iex

### Tradier (Options Chains)
- Used for: Real-time options chain data for covered call candidate analysis
- Client: `backend/app/services/tradier_service.py`
- Required: Tradier account + API token (sandbox and production tokens are different)
- Sandbox base URL: `https://sandbox.tradier.com/v1/`
- Production base URL: `https://api.tradier.com/v1/`
- Key endpoints:
  - `GET /markets/quotes` — live quotes
  - `GET /markets/options/chains` — full options chain by expiration
  - `GET /markets/options/expirations` — available expiration dates

