## Trading Rules Engine

All covered call filtering logic lives in `backend/app/core/trading_rules.py`.

### Covered Call Candidate Rules

| Rule                  | Condition                                                   |
|-----------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------|
| Green day             | Stock price > previous close                                |
| Minimum move          | Price up ≥ 0.8% on the day                                  |
| Profit target         | Target 80% of max premium (close at 20% of credit received) |
| Cost basis protection | Never sell a call below the position's average cost basis   |

