## Key Business Rules

- **Never sell a covered call below cost basis** — always check `positions.avg_cost` before surfacing a strike as a candidate
- **80% profit target** — dashboard should flag open covered calls when they've decayed to 20% of original premium
- **Green day + 0.8% filter** — only surface candidates on qualifying up days; do not show all tickers every day
- **Tradier sandbox vs. production** — use sandbox for all development; only switch to production token for live trading use
- **Positions table is the source of truth** — never hardcode share counts or cost basis in application logic

