## Testing Standards

- Backend: `pytest` with `httpx` async test client
- Mock Tiingo and Tradier API responses in all tests — never hit live APIs in CI
- Rule engine tests must cover: green day pass/fail, cost basis guard, 0.8% threshold edge cases
- Frontend: `Vitest` + `React Testing Library`

